OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FSexual harassment remains "shockingly"
OL,8,Fprevalent in the City, according to a
OL,9,Fcommittee of MPs.
OL,11,FMembers of the Treasury select
OL,12,Fcommittee say they were "appalled" by
OL,13,Fthe stories they heard from women
OL,14,Fworking in the City.
OL,16,FThe MPs warned that efforts to tackle
OL,17,Fsexism in the City were moving at a
OL,18,F"snail's pace" and said companies were
OL,19,Fhandling allegations of such behaviour
OL,20,Fpoorly.
