OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe politicians called for fresh
OL,8,Flegislation to ban the use of non-
OL,9,Fdisclosure agreements - that gag
OL,10,Fworkers who have faced mistreatment -
OL,11,Fafter discovering how widespread they
OL,12,Fwere.
OL,14,FIn their report entitled Sexism in the
OL,15,FCity, the MPs describe NDA's being
OL,16,Fused to cover up abuse, sexual
OL,17,Fharassment and discrimination.
