OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,8,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,9,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,10,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,12,FEvidence also suggested that 70 per
OL,13,Fcent of whistleblowers were
OL,14,Fvictimised, sacked or felt forced to
OL,15,Fresign.
OL,17,FThe report concludes that while sexual
OL,18,Fharassment against women is a societal
OL,19,Fproblem, it is worse in financial
OL,20,Fservices.
