OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe MPs demand a "zero-tolerance
OL,8,Fapproach", and warn that the overall
OL,9,Fculture prevalent in the City is
OL,10,Fholding women back.
OL,12,FHarriett Baldwin, the Conservative MP
OL,13,Fwho chairs the committee, said: "The
OL,14,FUK's financial services sector is the
OL,15,Fcrown jewel of this country's economy
OL,16,F` admired by the international
OL,17,Fcommunity and always takes pride in
OL,18,Fbeing ahead of the curve.
