OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"This well-paid sector will only be
OL,8,Fable to maintain its competitive
OL,9,Fadvantage if it is able to draw on the
OL,10,Fwidest possible pool of talent.
OL,12,F"That's why it's so frustrating that
OL,13,Fefforts to tackle sexism in the city
OL,14,Fare moving at a snail's pace."
OL,16,FShe said companies must take
OL,17,Fresponsibility for changing a culture
OL,18,F- which the report said was holding
OL,19,Fwomen back.
