OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FInaction was both "immoral" and "bad
OL,8,Ffor growth and business", she argued.
OL,10,FThe MPs also found evidence of
OL,11,Fperpetrators well known within their
OL,12,Forganisations for serial offending
OL,13,Fbeing effectively given immunity.
OL,15,FThe study did find some positive signs
OL,16,Fof improvement in the senior
OL,17,Frepresentation of women in some firms
OL,18,Fbut warned that progress was still
OL,19,F"too slow and patchy".
