OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThey also highlighted the problem of
OL,8,Fwomen struggling to succeed after
OL,9,Fhaving children.
OL,11,FThey praised the introduction of
OL,12,Fparental leave - including in some
OL,13,Fmajor firms - but argued the offer was
OL,14,Fstill not widespread across the
OL,15,Findustry.
