OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"We recommend that the Government and
OL,8,Fregulators encourage all firms to
OL,9,Fconsider equalising their offer of
OL,10,Fparental leave for men and women, and
OL,11,Fto actively encourage more men to take
OL,12,Fit up."
OL,14,FHybrid working as a result of Covid
OL,15,Fhad provided opportunities for women
OL,16,Fwith caring responsibilities, they
OL,17,Fsaid, warning that a push back to
OL,18,F"presenteeist" cultures could damage
OL,19,Fthat progress.
