OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThey also argued that as more people
OL,8,Freturn to the office, companies should
OL,9,Fbe careful to treat those who work
OL,10,Ffrom home more often - equally.
OL,12,F"We recommend that the Government and
OL,13,Fregulators encourage firms to
OL,14,Fadvertise as many roles as possible to
OL,15,Fbe available on flexible and part-time
OL,16,Fbases, as a way to attract and retain
OL,17,Fas wide a talent pool as possible,
OL,18,Fespecially women."
