OL,3,CSexism in the City: Harassment is
OL,4,C'shockingly' present in finance, MPs
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThey also called for even more focus
OL,8,Fon the impact of menopause, and
OL,9,Fpolicies to support women affected to
OL,10,Fprevent them being prematurely lost
OL,11,Ffrom the industry
OL,13,FAnd while they acknowledged the City
OL,14,Fis well-paid, they said the gender gap
OL,15,Fwas bigger than in any other sector
OL,16,Fand being reduced at a "glacial pace"
OL,17,Fwhich could take 70 years to close the
OL,18,Fgap.
